5) Write a program to count the frequency of numbers in a list 
Code:

n=int(input("enter no of elements"))
list=[]
for i in range(n):
    num=int(input("enter num"))
    list.append(num)
freq={}    
for num in list:
    if num in freq:
        freq[num]=freq[num]+1
    else:
        freq[num]=1
print("frequency of numbers in a list:",freq[num])
for key in freq:
    print(key,":",freq[key])

